Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.09,0:01:27.52,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}蕙芷芬芳 色状霓虹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.17,0:01:30.72,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}向阳步道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:35.81,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}鹿撞愈疾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:42.94,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}散学廊下 钟声回响
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.38,0:01:46.34,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}无奇世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:50.75,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}渐始闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:57.47,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}走而出者 慕君之思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:02:03.48,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}眼底心内 如系如缚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:09.30,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}心潮难平 盈溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:15.43,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}重之以君意 可与我知否
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:18.35,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}此心君可解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:21.26,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}此意望君知
